Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.82,0:24:48.25,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The ticket is all that I have lost
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.82,0:24:48.25,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}這張票是我已失去的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.24,0:24:52.15,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}十分な喪失と招待され
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.24,0:24:52.15,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那是讓人失去一切的招待
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.46,0:24:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,雷姆…呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.27,0:24:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,雷姆  怎麼樣了…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.30,0:24:54.83,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Today's program is a tragedy
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.30,0:24:54.83,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}今天在上演的是一齣悲劇
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.68,0:24:58.80,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}救済の一切もない名作を
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.68,0:24:58.80,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那是毫無救濟的名作
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.69,0:25:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,對了  雷姆  雷姆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.93,0:25:05.06,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Please be quiet. Hope is noisy
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.93,0:25:05.06,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}希望過於嘈雜  請安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.03,0:25:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,雷姆
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.55,0:25:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,雷姆  雷姆
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.89,0:25:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,雷姆…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.70,0:25:08.27,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The dreams rot off and drop away
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.70,0:25:08.27,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那些幻夢早已消失殆盡
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.88,0:25:12.00,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}望みこそ腐敗の元凶
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.88,0:25:12.00,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}希望正是腐敗的元兇
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.04,0:25:14.89,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}No wish, no smile, only despair
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.04,0:25:14.89,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}禁止許願  禁止歡笑  只有絕望
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.50,0:25:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,所以請昴在這裡等雷姆回來
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.91,0:25:18.73,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The curtain will open
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.91,0:25:18.73,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}大幕將要拉開
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.40,0:25:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,等我將一切解決後
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.99,0:25:21.79,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Welcome to the party
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.99,0:25:21.79,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}歡迎來到這個派對
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.96,0:25:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,一定會回來接你的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.90,0:25:25.51,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}暗闇で舞う無数の影よ
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.90,0:25:25.51,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}在漆黑中起舞的眾多黑影
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.23,0:25:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,請多保重
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.27,0:25:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,在我回來前  拜託你一定在那裡等著我
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.65,0:25:28.42,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}This show will never end
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.65,0:25:28.42,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}這齣戲將永不落幕
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.58,0:25:35.44,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}何人も逃れられはしない
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.58,0:25:35.44,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}沒有人能從中脫身解救
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.36,0:25:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.19,0:25:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,昴的…雷姆敬上
